852
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,760
You don't understand.

853
00:34:29,871 --> 00:34:31,150
And you, why are you laughing?

854
00:34:31,159 --> 00:34:31,880
You're no better,

855
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:33,159
never care about anything!

856
00:34:33,479 --> 00:34:34,479
I'm telling you both,

857
00:34:35,240 --> 00:34:36,760
this is serious.

858
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:40,639
Shen Mingzhu didn't
even tell us about this.

859
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:43,559
Do you know what that means?

860
00:34:43,559 --> 00:34:44,760
What does it mean?

861
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:48,240
It means Shen Mingzhu's loyalty

862
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,240
is wavering.

863
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,960
It means

864
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:54,960
she doesn't see us as her own family.

865
00:35:00,679 --> 00:35:01,760
I regret it now.

866
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:04,599
I never should've given her

867
00:35:04,599 --> 00:35:06,639
that heirloom bracelet so early.

868
00:35:07,479 --> 00:35:09,320
Yes, you should've
given it to me instead.

869
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:09,880
That's enough.

870
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:11,599
Don't butt in.

871
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,679
What's done is done.

872
00:35:16,599 --> 00:35:17,479
And anyway,

873
00:35:17,479 --> 00:35:19,159
even if Mingzhu's feelings are divided,

874
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:21,079
she's still carrying

875
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,119
our family's grandchild, isn't she?

876
00:35:23,519 --> 00:35:26,320
Precisely because
she's carrying our grandchild,

877
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,800
she must stay absolutely loyal to us.

878
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:30,079
Oh my god, Mom,

879
00:35:30,079 --> 00:35:32,800
you can control everything
but not someone's heart.

880
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:33,360
That's right.

881
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:34,426
What do you mean by that?

882
00:35:35,293 --> 00:35:36,070
What does that mean?

883
00:35:36,119 --> 00:35:38,020
Does Shen Mingzhu
have something else going on

884
00:35:38,026 --> 00:35:39,471
that you're not telling me? Tell me!

885
00:35:39,479 --> 00:35:40,479
Nothing.

886
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,070
You're being irrational.

887
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:43,604
I'm not telling you anything anymore.

888
00:35:43,679 --> 00:35:44,639
Oh no, listen now,

889
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:45,760
you're telling me everything.

890
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:48,559
From now on, any little sign,

891
00:35:48,559 --> 00:35:50,629
rumor, or whisper,
you report it to me immediately.

892
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:52,493
That's called prevention
before trouble starts!

893
00:35:53,604 --> 00:35:54,804
I'm going to take a bath.

894
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:58,440
Feng.

895
00:35:59,159 --> 00:35:59,800
Feng.

896
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,360
I'm coming now.

897
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:01,960
Right over.

898
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,920
Something has come up at the factory.

899
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:04,720
I have to be there.

900
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:05,760
At this hour?

901
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,720
What came up?

902
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:07,479
Where are you going?

903
00:36:07,479 --> 00:36:08,679
The factory.

904
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:22,880
Mingzhu.

905
00:36:24,479 --> 00:36:25,119
Mom?

906
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:26,800
You're still awake?

907
00:36:28,160 --> 00:36:29,110
I was waiting for you.

908
00:36:30,479 --> 00:36:31,320
Me?

909
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,679
I heard

910
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,800
you found your birth parents.

911
00:36:40,559 --> 00:36:41,240
Yes.

912
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,960
Why didn't you tell us?

913
00:36:46,199 --> 00:36:48,079
It happened just a few days ago.

914
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,639
I haven't had the chance.

915
00:36:50,599 --> 00:36:51,720
We see each other everyday,

916
00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:53,240
morning and night.

917
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:54,604
You haven't had the chance?

918
00:36:55,079 --> 00:36:55,840
I don't think so.

919
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,880
Did you not want to tell me?

920
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:02,070
Do you really see this place
as your home?

921
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,800
Do you really see us as your family?

922
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:08,479
Actually,

923
00:37:09,119 --> 00:37:11,119
