with you and Bichen...

996
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,280
That's impossible.

997
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,720
I know it's impossible!

998
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:43,240
I'm just talking about a "what if",

999
00:40:43,679 --> 00:40:44,320
right?

1000
00:40:45,915 --> 00:40:48,550
It's much harder to get money
back than it is to give it away.

1001
00:40:49,079 --> 00:40:50,159
Alright, don't worry.

1002
00:40:50,479 --> 00:40:51,840
Your mother knows what she's doing.

1003
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:52,599
Okay.

1004
00:40:52,648 --> 00:40:53,630
Just wish me the best.

1005
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:54,629
Alright!

1006
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:55,537
Off to buy groceries?

1007
