1012
00:41:05,337 --> 00:41:07,440
Soon, Madam Zheng. I'll send you
an invitation when it's time.

1013
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:08,639
Alright, I'll be waiting!

1014
00:41:08,639 --> 00:41:11,199
A son's wedding will
be the death of his father!

1015
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:12,960
But it's a happy occasion!

1016
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,320
The exhaustion is worth it!

1017
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,920
That's right.

1018
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,639
Easy there.

1019
00:41:16,639 --> 00:41:17,479
Careful.

1020
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:19,119
I got in.

1021
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:22,240
Alright!

1022
00:41:25,060 --> 00:41:29,300
(Nanzhou First People's Hospital)

1023
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:30,960
The test results are good.

1024
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,937
Nothing to worry about.

1025
00:41:32,004 --> 00:41:34,004
I've been busy planning
a wedding banquet lately.

1026
00:41:34,004 --> 00:41:34,960
Strangely, keeping busy

1027
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,559
has helped me eat and sleep better.

1028
00:41:36,560 --> 00:41:38,226
Because you're
keeping yourself occupied.

1029
00:41:38,248 --> 00:41:39,620
But still, don't overwork yourself.

1030
00:41:40,671 --> 00:41:42,440
By the way, I wanted
to ask you something.

1031
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,280
My uncle is turning 70 next month.

1032
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:46,115
Does Nanxi Hotel
handle birthday banquets?

1033
00:41:46,137 --> 00:41:47,093
Of course we do!

1034
00:41:47,226 --> 00:41:49,320
If you book with us,
I'll get a discount for you.

1035
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,693
Great, I'll let the family know.

1036
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:52,880
I'll visit your hotel this weekend
to take a look first.

1037
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,960
Sure, no problem.

1038
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,400
Just call me before you come.

1039
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,199
Sure.

1040
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:56,920
I'm done.

1041
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:57,720
Take care.

1042
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:58,400
Bye.

1043
